[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 441     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m **Step 6: Export to clinical systems.** The fused results need to flow back into clinical systems in formats they understand. For radiation oncology, this means DICOM-RT Structure Sets (contours) and DICOM-RT Dose files. For surgical navigation, it might be 3D surface meshes or proprietary formats. This step converts the computational output into clinically consumable formats and pushes them back to the DICOM store where treatment planning systems can retrieve them.
