[0m[49m[39m  518, 568[0m:[39m[49m **Performance benchmarks:**
[0m[49m[39m  519, 569[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[39m  520, 570[0m:[39m[49m | Metric | Typical Value |
[0m[49m[39m  521, 571[0m:[39m[49m |--------|---------------|
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 522     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | Rigid registration (brain) | 5-15 seconds |
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 523     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m | Deformable registration (abdomen) | 10-60 seconds (DL) / 5-30 minutes (classical) |
